==German==

===Conjunction===
'''daß'''

# [[that]]

====Usage notes====
The spelling of "daß" was changed to '''[[dass]]''' by the 1996 spelling reform ''([[Rechtschreibreform]])'', which is mandatory in public schools and government offices, but ignored by many in the private sector, including some of Germany’s most respected newspapers.

